graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Fetch Sitemap Index]
    B --> C{Monthly Sitemaps Found?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Fetch Article URLs]
    C -->|No| E[End]
    D --> F[Scrape Article Content & Metadata]
    F --> G{Valid Article?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Save Article Data]
    G -->|No| D
    H --> I{Max Articles Scraped?}
    I -->|Yes| E
    I -->|No| D
